Early preview v0.1
The schematic below illustrates high-level architecture and data flows that meet the following criteria:

On a national scale (spanning all NHS regions);
Occur electronically (data is managed electronically and systematically collected via API);
Managed systematically (the same documented process is reproduced across all extractions and transfers).

Each category of data flows below can be toggled. The diagram may take 30 seconds to load. Best viewed in desktop/laptop computer web browser, and in full screen.
